NK046(mi)003:1: // byang chub sems dpa'i spyod pa la 'jug pa'i sa bcad don gsal me long bzhugs so //
NK046(mi)003:2: dus gsum gyi rgyal ba thams cad kyi gshegs shing
NK046(mi)003:3: rjes su gshegs pa'i bgrod pa gcig pa'i lam po
NK046(mi)003:4: che phan bde ma lus pa sgrub pa'i rgyu gcig
NK046(mi)003:5: pur gyur pa / srid zhi'i legs tshogs thams cad kyi 'byung gnas /
NK046(mi)003:6: rin chen byang chub kyi sems gtso bor ston pa /
NK046(mi)003:7: rgyal sras byang chub sems dpa'i spyod pa la 'jug
NK046(mi)003:8: pa'i gzhung bzang yid bzhin gyi nor bu rin po
NK046(mi)003:9: che 'di nyid 'chad par byed pa la /
NK046(mi)003:10: bshad bya'i yan lag bshad pa dang /
NK046(mi)003:11: bshad bya dngos bshad pa ste gnyis su yod pa las /
NK046(mi)003:13: slob dpon gyis chos ji ltar 'chad tshul /
NK046(mi)003:15: dpon slob gnyis kas 'chad nyan ji ltar bgyid tshul
NK046(mi)003:16: te gsum du yod pa de dag bshad grub nas
NK046(mi)003:17: / gnyis pa bshad bya dngos la /
NK046(mi)003:19: mtshan de ldan gyi gzhung dngos bshad pa gnyis las /
NK046(mi)003:20: dang po la'ang mtshan dngos bshad pa dang /
NK046(mi)003:21: zhar byung du 'gyur phyag gnyis las /
NK046(mi)003:26: gnyis pa la'ang bstan bcos rtsom pa la 'jug pa'i
NK046(mi)003:27: rgyu brtsam bya bstan bcos lus kyi rang bzhin dngos
NK046(mi)003:28: dang / mjug yongs su rdzogs pa'i bya ba bshad pa dang gsum las /
NK046(mi)003:30: dang po mchod par brjod pa ni /
NK046(mi)003:31: bde gshegs chos kyi sogs rkang pa gnyis /
NK046(mi)003:32: gnyis pa brtsam par dam bca' ba ni /
NK046(mi)003:33: bde gshegs sras kyi sogs rkang pa gnyis /
NK046(mi)003:34: gsum pa khengs pa skyungs pa ni /
NK046(mi)003:35: sngon chad sogs sho lo ka gcig /
NK046(mi)003:36: bzhi pa spro ba bskyed pa ni /
NK046(mi)003:37: dge ba bsgom sogs sho lo ka gcig gis bstan to //
NK046(mi)003:38: gnyis pa brtsam bya bstan bcos lus kyi rang bzhin dngos bshad pa la /
NK046(mi)003:39: byang chub sems mchog rin po che //
NK046(mi)003:40: ma skyes pa rnams skye gyur cig /
NK046(mi)003:41: skyes pa nyams pa med par yang //
NK046(mi)003:42: gong nas gong du 'phel bar shog /
NK046(mi)003:44: kun rdzob dang don dam pa'i byang chub kyi sems
NK046(mi)003:45: rin po che rang rgyud la ma skyes pa bskyed
NK046(mi)003:47: skyes pa mi nyams par byed pa'i le'u gsum /
NK046(mi)003:48: mi nyams par gong nas gong du 'phel bar byed pa'i le'u gsum /
NK046(mi)003:49: de ltar spel ba'i 'bras bu gzhan don la bsngo ba dang smon pa'i le'u gcig ste /
NK046(mi)003:50: gzhung le'u bcu'i rang bzhin sa bcad bzhis yongs su bsdus te 'chad par byed pa las /
NK046(mi)003:51: dang po byang chub kyi sems rin po che rang
NK046(mi)003:52: rgyud la ma skyes pa bskyed par byed pa'i le'u
NK046(mi)003:53: gsum ni / dang po phan yon gyi sgo nas brod pa skyed pa'i le'u /
NK046(mi)003:54: gnyis pa mi mthun phyogs kyi sdig pa bshags pa'i le'u /
NK046(mi)003:55: gsum pa mthun phyogs byang sems yongs bzung gi le'u dang gsum las /
NK046(mi)003:56: dang po phan yon gyi le'u la gzhung dang /
NK046(mi)003:59: byang chub sems kyi rten bshad pa dang /
NK046(mi)003:60: phan yon bshad pa gnyis las /
NK046(mi)003:62: lus rten dang sems rten bshad pa gnyis las /
NK046(mi)003:64: dal 'byor sogs shwa lo ka gcig /
NK046(mi)003:66: ji ltar mtshan mo sogs shwa lo ka gcig /
NK046(mi)003:68: sems bskyed spyi yi phan yon /
NK046(mi)003:70: sems bskyed rgyud ldan gyi gang zag gi che ba bshad pa dang gsum las /
NK046(mi)003:72: dge ba gzhan las khyad par du 'phags pa'i phan yon /
NK046(mi)003:73: ming don gnas 'gyur ba'i phan yon /
NK046(mi)003:74: phan yon dpe'i sgo nas bstan pa dang gsum las /
NK046(mi)003:76: de ltas dge ba sogs tshigs bcad gsum /
NK046(mi)003:78: byang chub sems skyes sogs tshigs bcad gcig /
NK046(mi)003:79: gsum pa la'ang gser 'gyur gyi dpes sangs rgyas thob par bstan pa /
NK046(mi)003:80: rin po che'i dpes don che bar bstan pa /
NK046(mi)003:81: 'bras bu can gyi ljon shing gi dpes dge rtsa mi zad cing gong du 'phel bar bstan pa /
NK046(mi)003:82: skyel ma dpa' bo'i dpes nges pa'i sdig pa zil gyis gnon par bstan pa /
NK046(mi)003:83: dus mtha'i me'i dpes ma nges pa'i sdig pa drung nas 'byin par bstan pa /
NK046(mi)003:84: 'dir ma bshad pa gzhan du zhal 'phangs pa dang drug las /
NK046(mi)003:86: gser 'gyur sogs sho lo ka gcig /
NK046(mi)003:88: 'gro ba'i sogs shwa lo ka gcig /
NK046(mi)003:90: dge ba sogs tshigs bcad gcig /
NK046(mi)003:92: sdig pa sogs tshigs bcad gcig /
NK046(mi)003:94: des ni sogs rkang pa gnyis /
NK046(mi)003:96: de yi sogs rkang pa gnyis kyis bstan to //
NK046(mi)003:97: gnyis pa smon 'jug so so'i phan yon la /
NK046(mi)003:100: lung rigs kyi sgo nas sgrub pa dang gsum las /
NK046(mi)003:102: byang chub sems de sogs sho lo ka gnyis /
NK046(mi)003:104: byang chub smon pa'i sogs tshigs bcad gsum /
NK046(mi)003:106: lung dang rigs pa'i sgo nas sgrub pa gnyis las /
NK046(mi)003:109: gnyis pa rigs pas sgrub pa la'ang smon pa'i phan yon dang /
NK046(mi)003:110: 'jug pa'i phan yon rigs pas sgrub pa gnyis las /
NK046(mi)003:112: sems can rnams kyi sogs tshigs bcad drug /
NK046(mi)003:114: phan par bsam pa sogs tshigs bcad bzhi /
NK046(mi)003:115: gsum pa sems bskyed rgyud ldan gyi gang zag gi che ba bshad pa ni /
NK046(mi)003:116: phan btags lan sogs tshigs bcad drug gis bstan zin to //
NK046(mi)003:120: gnyis pa byang chub sems kyi mi mthun phyogs sdig pa bshags pa'i le'u la'ang /
NK046(mi)003:123: dang po la'ang mchod pa'i yan lag /
NK046(mi)003:126: sdig pa bshags pa'i yan lag dang bzhi las /
NK046(mi)003:129: yid kyis sprul pa'i mchod pa /
NK046(mi)003:130: smon lam stobs kyi mchod pa /
NK046(mi)003:131: bla na med pa'i mchod pa /
NK046(mi)003:132: bstod pa dbyangs kyi mchod pa dang lnga las /
NK046(mi)003:134: bdag pos yongs su bzung ba'i mchod pa dang /
NK046(mi)003:136: lus dbul ba'i mchod pa dang gsum las /
NK046(mi)003:138: rin chen sems de sogs tshigs bcad gcig /
NK046(mi)003:140: me tog 'bras bu sogs tshigs bcad drug /
NK046(mi)003:142: rgyal dang de sras sogs tshigs bcad gnyis /
NK046(mi)003:144: khrus dang sku phyi sogs kyi mchod pa dang /
NK046(mi)003:145: nyer spyod kyi mchod pa gnyis las /
NK046(mi)003:147: khrus kyi khang pa sogs tshigs bcad bzhi /
NK046(mi)003:149: stong gsum sogs tshigs bcad drug /
NK046(mi)003:150: gsum pa smon lam stobs kyi mchod pa ni /
NK046(mi)003:151: de las sogs tshigs bcad gnyis /
NK046(mi)003:152: bzhi pa bla na med pa'i mchod pa ni /
NK046(mi)003:153: ji ltar sogs tshigs bcad gcig /
NK046(mi)003:154: lnga pa bstod pa dbyangs kyi mchod pa ni /
NK046(mi)003:155: yon tan sogs tshigs bcad gcig /
NK046(mi)003:156: gnyis pa phyag 'tshal ba'i yan lag ni /
NK046(mi)003:157: dus gsum gshegs pa'i sogs tshigs bcad gnyis /
NK046(mi)003:158: gsum pa skyabs su 'gro ba'i yan lag ni /
NK046(mi)003:159: byang chub sogs tshigs bcad gcig /
NK046(mi)003:160: bzhi pa sdig pa bshags pa'i yan lag la /
NK046(mi)003:161: bshags yul mngon du bya ba dang /
NK046(mi)003:162: bshags pa dngos bshad pa gnyis las /
NK046(mi)003:164: phyogs rnams sogs tshigs bcad gcig /
NK046(mi)003:168: gnyen po kun tu spyod pa'i stobs dang /
NK046(mi)003:169: sor chud pa'i stobs dang bzhi las /
NK046(mi)003:171: thog ma sogs tshigs bcad bcu dgu /
NK046(mi)003:173: de bas rgyal ba sogs tshigs bcad bdun /
NK046(mi)003:175: gnyen po brten dgos pa'i rgyu mtshan dang /
NK046(mi)003:178: tha ma la sogs tshigs bcad dgu /
NK046(mi)003:180: bdag ni mi shes sogs tshigs bcad gnyis /
NK046(mi)003:182: 'dren pa sogs tshigs bcad gcig gis bstan to //
NK046(mi)003:187: // gsum pa mthun phyogs byang sems yongs bzung gi le'u la /
NK046(mi)003:190: sbyor ba sngon du 'gro ba'i chos /
NK046(mi)003:192: mjug rang gzhan dga' ba sgom pa dang gsum las /
NK046(mi)003:193: dang po la'ang byang chub kyi sems rin po che
NK046(mi)003:194: rang rgyud la bskyed pa'i lhan cig byed pa'i rkyen
NK046(mi)003:196: nyer len gyi rgyu blo sbyang ba gnyis las /
NK046(mi)003:199: mchod phyag skyabs 'gro sdig bshags kyi yan lag bzhi le'u gnyis pa'i skabs su bshad zin nas /
NK046(mi)003:201: rjes su yi rang ba'i dang /
NK046(mi)003:202: chos 'khor bskor bar bskul ba'i gsol ba 'debs pa'i dang /
NK046(mi)003:203: mya ngan las mi 'da' bar bzhugs par gsol ba 'debs pa'i dang /
NK046(mi)003:204: dge rtsa gzhan don du bsngo ba'i yan lag dang bzhi las /
NK046(mi)003:206: sems can kun gyi sogs tshigs bcad gsum dang rkang pa gnyis /
NK046(mi)003:208: phyogs rnams sogs tshigs bcad gcig /
NK046(mi)003:210: rgyal ba sogs tshigs bcad gcig /
NK046(mi)003:212: de ltar 'di dag sogs tshigs bcad bzhi /
NK046(mi)003:216: lus bye brag tu gtong ba /
NK046(mi)003:217: blo sbyong gi 'bras bu gzhan don du smon lam btab pa dang bzhi las /
NK046(mi)003:219: lus dang sogs tshigs bcad gcig /
NK046(mi)003:221: thams cad btang bas sogs tshigs bcad gcig /
NK046(mi)003:223: bdag gis lus can sogs tshigs bcad gnyis /
NK046(mi)003:225: de la gnod par sogs tshigs bcad brgyad dang rkang pa gcig /
NK046(mi)003:226: gnyis pa dngos gzhi dam bca' ba ni /
NK046(mi)003:227: ji ltar sogs tshigs bcad gnyis /
NK046(mi)003:228: gsum pa mjug tu rang gzhan dga' ba sgom pa la /
NK046(mi)003:229: rang dga' ba sgom pa dang /
NK046(mi)003:230: gzhan dga' ba sgom du gzhug pa dang gnyis las /
NK046(mi)003:232: de ltar blo dang sogs tshigs bcad dgu /
NK046(mi)003:234: bdag gis de ring sogs tshigs bcad gcig gis bstan to //
NK046(mi)003:239: // gnyis pa skyes pa mi nyams par byed pa la /
NK046(mi)003:240: 'jug ldog gi gnas la gzob pa lhur len pa bag yod kyi le'u /
NK046(mi)003:241: rang gi sgo gsum la brtags pa shes bzhin gyi le'u /
NK046(mi)003:242: byang chub sems kyi bye brag gi mi mthun phyogs
NK046(mi)003:243: khong khro'i gnyen po bzod pa'i le'u dang gsum las
NK046(mi)003:244: / dang po bag yod kyi le'u la /
NK046(mi)003:247: dang po la'ang mdor bstan pa dang /
NK046(mi)003:248: rgyas par bshad pa gnyis las /
NK046(mi)003:250: rgyal ba'i sogs tshigs bcad gcig /
NK046(mi)003:252: sgrub bya bslab pa la bsams te bag bya ba /
NK046(mi)003:253: rten dal 'byor la bsams te bag bya ba /
NK046(mi)003:254: spangs bya nyon mongs la bsams te bag bya ba dang gsum las /
NK046(mi)003:256: bsam pa byang chub sems bskyed mi nyams par bsrung ba dang /
NK046(mi)003:257: sbyor ba brtson 'grus mi nyams par bsrung ba dang gnyis las /
NK046(mi)003:259: bab col brtsams pa sogs tshigs bcad bcu /
NK046(mi)003:261: de ltar ji ltar sogs tshigs bcad gsum /
NK046(mi)003:263: dal 'byor rnyed daka'i tshul la bsams te bag bya ba /
NK046(mi)003:264: ngan song las thar dka' ba la bsams te bag bya ba /
NK046(mi)003:265: dal 'byor thob dus dge ba la 'bad dgos par bstan pa gsum las /
NK046(mi)003:267: de bzhin gshegs pa sogs tshigs bcad drug /
NK046(mi)003:269: skad cig gcig byas sogs tshigs bcad gnyis /
NK046(mi)003:271: 'di 'dra'i dal ba sogs tshigs bcad lnga /
NK046(mi)003:272: gsum pa spangs bya nyon mongs la bsams te bag bya ba la'ang /
NK046(mi)003:273: nyon mongs pa'i nyes dmigs bshad pa dang /
NK046(mi)003:274: nyon mongs pa spangs pa'i dka' spyad bzod pa /
NK046(mi)003:275: nyon mongs ji ltar spangs tshul dang gsum las /
NK046(mi)003:277: zhe sdang sogs tshigs bcad brgyad /
NK046(mi)003:279: de ltar ji srid sogs tshigs bcad bdun /
NK046(mi)003:281: 'di la bdag gis sogs tshigs bcad drug gis bstan to //
NK046(mi)003:286: // gnyis pa le'u lnga pa shes bzhin gyi le'u la'ang /
NK046(mi)003:290: bslab pa bsrung ba'i thabs su sems bsrung ba /
NK046(mi)003:291: sems bsrung ba'i thabs su dran shes brtan tshul /
NK046(mi)003:292: dran shes dang ldan pa'i sgo nas sems sbyong gi spyod pa la bslab tshul /
NK046(mi)003:293: bsgrub pa phun sum tshogs pa'i yan lag gzhan bstan pa dang bzhi las /
NK046(mi)003:295: mdor bstan pa dang rgyas par bshad pa gnyis las /
NK046(mi)003:297: bslab pa sogs tshigs bcad gcig /
NK046(mi)003:298: gnyis pa rgyas par bshad pa la'ang /
NK046(mi)003:299: gnod pa thams cad sems las byung tshul /
NK046(mi)003:300: dge ba thams cad sems las byung tshul /
NK046(mi)003:301: des na nges par sems bsrung dgos par bstan pa dang gsum las /
NK046(mi)003:303: sems kyi glang po sogs tshigs bcad bdun /
NK046(mi)003:305: gal te 'gro ba sogs tshigs bcad dgu /
NK046(mi)003:307: de ltas bdag gis sogs tshigs bcad lnga /
NK046(mi)003:308: gnyis pa sems bsrung ba'i thabs su dran shes brtan tshul la'ang /
NK046(mi)003:310: rgyas par bshad pa gnyis las /
NK046(mi)003:312: sems bsrung 'dod pa sogs tshigs bcad gcig /
NK046(mi)003:313: gnyis pa rgyas par bshad pa la'ang /
NK046(mi)003:314: shes bzhin med pa'i nyes dmigs bshad pa dang /
NK046(mi)003:315: dran pa brtan thabs dngos bshad pa gnyis las /
NK046(mi)003:317: nad kyis dkrugs pa'i sogs tshigs bcad lnga /
NK046(mi)003:319: de bas dran pa sogs tshigs bcad lnga /
NK046(mi)003:320: gsum pa sems sbyong gi spyod pa la bslab tshul la'ang /
NK046(mi)003:321: nyes spyod sdom pa'i tshul khrims la bslab tshul /
NK046(mi)003:322: dge ba chos sdud kyi tshul khrims la bslab tshul /
NK046(mi)003:323: sems can don byed kyi tshul khrims la bslab tshul dang gsum las /
NK046(mi)003:325: sgo gsum gyi spyod pa dag par bya ba dang /
NK046(mi)003:326: bslab pa nyams pa srung ba gnyis las /
NK046(mi)003:328: re shig dang por sogs tshigs bcad bcu gcig /
NK046(mi)003:330: bre mo'i gtam ni sogs tshigs bcad bcu bzhi /
NK046(mi)003:332: bslab pa la mi slob pa'i rgyu lus la chags pa spangs dgos par bstan pa dang /
NK046(mi)003:333: bsgrub pa'i thabs la mkhas par bya ba gnyis las /
NK046(mi)003:335: bya rgod sha la sogs tshigs bcad bcu gnyis /
NK046(mi)003:337: de lta rang dbang sogs tshigs bcad bcu gsum /
NK046(mi)003:340: zang zing dang chos kyis bsdu ba /
NK046(mi)003:341: pha rol gyi ma dad pa bsrung pa dang gsum las /
NK046(mi)003:343: de ltar rig byas sogs tshigs bcad gcig /
NK046(mi)003:345: log par ltung dang sogs tshigs bcad drug /
NK046(mi)003:347: so shing dang ni sogs tshigs bcad drug /
NK046(mi)003:348: bzhi pa bsgrub pa phun sum tshogs pa'i yan lag gzhan bstan pa la'ang /
NK046(mi)003:349: bsgrub pa phun sum tshogs pa'i yan lag dngos dang /
NK046(mi)003:350: ngo bo ngos bzung nas le'u'i don bsdu ba gnyis las /
NK046(mi)003:352: byang chub sems dpa'i sogs tshigs bcad bcu gcig /
NK046(mi)003:354: lus dang sems sogs tshigs bcad gnyis kyis bstan to //
NK046(mi)003:359: // gsum pa le'u drug pa bzod pa'i le'u la'ang /
NK046(mi)003:364: sems can la gus par bya ba dang gsum las /
NK046(mi)003:366: bskal pa stong du sogs tshigs bcad bcu /
NK046(mi)003:368: bzod yul ngos bzung ba dang /
NK046(mi)003:369: bzod pa bsgom pa dngos gnyis las /
NK046(mi)003:371: bdag gam bdag gi sogs tshigs bcad gcig /
NK046(mi)003:373: mi 'dod pa byed pa la bzod pa sgom pa dang /
NK046(mi)003:374: 'dod pa'i gegs byed pa la bzod pa bsgom pa dang gnyis las /
NK046(mi)003:376: bdag la sdug bsngal byed pa la bzod pa dang /
NK046(mi)003:377: bdag la brnyas sogs byed pa la bzod pa dang /
NK046(mi)003:378: bdag gi bshes la mi 'dod pa byed pa la bzod pa dang /
NK046(mi)003:379: bdag gi dgra la legs par byed pa la bzod pa dang bzhi las /
NK046(mi)003:381: sdug bsngal dang len gyi bzod pa dang /
NK046(mi)003:382: chos la nges sems kyi bzod pa dang /
NK046(mi)003:383: gnod byed la ji mi snyam pa'i bzod pa dang gsum las /
NK046(mi)003:385: bde ba'i rgyu ni sogs tshigs bcad bcu /
NK046(mi)003:387: mkhris pa sogs tshigs bcad bcu gnyis /
NK046(mi)003:389: gal te rang dgas sogs tshigs bcad bco brgyad /
NK046(mi)003:391: yid ni lus can sogs tshigs bcad bcu gnyis /
NK046(mi)003:393: sku gzugs mchod rten sogs tshigs bcad bcu gnyis /
NK046(mi)003:395: gzhan gyis yon tan sogs tshigs bcad bcu gcig /
NK046(mi)003:396: gnyis pa 'dod pa'i gegs byed pa la bzod pa sgom pa de la yang /
NK046(mi)003:397: dgra bo'i mi 'dod pa'i gegs byed pa la bzod pa sgom pa dang /
NK046(mi)003:398: bdag dang bdag gi bshes la 'dod pa'i bgegs byed pa la bzod pa bsgom pa dang gnyis las /
NK046(mi)003:400: gal te dgra zhig sogs tshigs bcad gsum /
NK046(mi)003:402: bstod dang grags pa'i sogs tshigs bcad nyer gnyis /
NK046(mi)003:403: gsum pa sems can la gus par bya ba la'ang /
NK046(mi)003:404: bsod nams kyi zhing du bsams te gus par bya ba dang /
NK046(mi)003:405: rgyal ba dgyes pa la bsams te gus par bya ba dang /
NK046(mi)003:406: phan gnod kyi 'bras bu la bsams te gus par bya ba dang gsum las /
NK046(mi)003:408: de phyir sogs tshigs bcad bdun /
NK046(mi)003:410: gzhan yang sogs tshigs bcad dgu /
NK046(mi)003:412: dper na rgyal po'i sogs tshigs bcad bdun gyis bstan to //
NK046(mi)003:417: // gsum pa mi nyams par gong nas gong du 'phel bar byed pa la /
NK046(mi)003:418: kun rdzob dang don dam pa'i byang chub kyi sems
NK046(mi)003:419: rnam pa gnyis gong nas gong du 'phel ba'i thabs
NK046(mi)003:420: sam grogs su gyur pa brtson 'grus kyi le'u /
NK046(mi)003:421: kun rdzob sems bskyed gong nas gong du 'phel bar byed pa bsam gtan gyi le'u /
NK046(mi)003:422: don dam sems bskyed gong nas gong du 'phel bar byed pa shes rab kyi le'u dang gsum las /
NK046(mi)003:423: dang po brtson 'grus kyi le'u la /
NK046(mi)003:427: brtson 'grus brtsom dgos pa'i rgyu mtshan mdor bstan pa dang /
NK046(mi)003:428: ji ltar rtsom tshul rgyas par bshad pa dang gnyis las /
NK046(mi)003:430: de ltar bzod pas sogs tshigs bcad gcig /
NK046(mi)003:432: brtson 'grus kyi ngo bo ngos bzung ba dang /
NK046(mi)003:433: brtson 'grus kyi mi mthun phyogs spangs pa dang /
NK046(mi)003:434: mthun phyogs sgrub pa ste gsum las /
NK046(mi)003:436: brtson gang dge la spro ba'o //
NK046(mi)003:439: mi mthun pa'i phyogs le lo rgyu 'bras dang bcas pa ngos bzung ba dang /
NK046(mi)003:440: de ji ltar spong thabs kyi gnyen po bshad pa gnyis las /
NK046(mi)003:442: de yi mi sogs tshigs bcad gcig dang rkang pa gsum /
NK046(mi)003:444: snyoms las 'dzin pa'i le lo'i gnyen po sgom tshul dang /
NK046(mi)003:445: bya ba ngan zhen gyi le lo'i gnyen po sgom tshul dang /
NK046(mi)003:446: sgyid lugs kyi le lo'i gnyen po sgom tshul bshad pa dang gsum las /
NK046(mi)003:448: nyon mongs rgya bas sogs tshigs bcad bcu gcig /
NK046(mi)003:450: dga' ba'i rgyu ni sogs tshigs bcad gnyis /
NK046(mi)003:452: bdag gis byang chub sogs tshigs bcad bco lnga /
NK046(mi)003:453: gsum pa mthun phyogs sgrub pa la /
NK046(mi)003:457: de ltar mi mthun sogs tshigs bcad gcig /
NK046(mi)003:460: stobs gnyis bskyed tshul bshad pa dang gnyis las /
NK046(mi)003:463: brtan pa'am nga rgyal gyi dpung bshad pa /
NK046(mi)003:465: dor ba'i dpung bshad pa dang bzhi las /
NK046(mi)003:467: bdag dang gzhan gyi sogs tshigs bcad bcu gsum dang rkang pa gnyis /
NK046(mi)003:469: spyir bshad pa dang bye brag tu bshad pa gnyis las /
NK046(mi)003:471: rdo rje rgyal mtshan sogs tshigs bcad gsum /
NK046(mi)003:475: nyon mongs pa'i nga rgyal dang gsum las /
NK046(mi)003:477: bdag nyid gcig pus sogs tshigs rkang bcu /
NK046(mi)003:479: shi ba'i sprul dang sogs tshigs bcad brgyad dang rkang pa gcig /
NK046(mi)003:481: nyon mongs phyogs kyi sogs tshigs bcad gsum /
NK046(mi)003:483: de bzhin gnas skabs sogs tshigs bcad bzhi dang rkang pa gnyis /
NK046(mi)003:485: stobs nyams pa dang sogs tshigs bcad gcig /
NK046(mi)003:486: gnyis pa stobs gnyis bskyed tshul la'ang /
NK046(mi)003:488: dbang bsgyur gyi stobs gnyis las /
NK046(mi)003:490: 'thab rnying dgra dang sogs tshigs bcad bdun /
NK046(mi)003:492: ci nas las byed sogs tshigs bcad gnyis kyis bstan to //
NK046(mi)003:497: // gnyis pa le'u brgyad pa bsam gtan gyi le'u la gzhung dang /
NK046(mi)003:500: mtshams sbyor ba'i sgo nas mdor bstan pa /
NK046(mi)003:501: bsam gtan gyi mi mthun phyogs spangs pa /
NK046(mi)003:502: bsam gtan sgom pa dngos dang gsum las /
NK046(mi)003:504: de ltar brtson 'grus sogs tshigs bcad gcig /
NK046(mi)003:509: lus dang sems ni sogs tshigs bcad gcig /
NK046(mi)003:512: rnam rtog dor ba gnyis las /
NK046(mi)003:514: 'jig rten spangs dgos pa'i rgyu mtshan bshad pa dang /
NK046(mi)003:515: nang sems can gyi 'jig rten la chags pa spangs par bya ba dang /
NK046(mi)003:516: phyi rnyed sogs kyi 'jig rten la sred pa spangs par bya ba dang /
NK046(mi)003:517: spangs nas dben pa brten tshul bshad pa dang bzhi las /
NK046(mi)003:519: chags pa'i phyir dang sogs tshigs bcad gnyis /
NK046(mi)003:521: mi rtags su zhig sogs tshigs bcad bcu gnyis /
NK046(mi)003:523: bdag ni rnyed mang sogs tshigs bcad brgyad /
NK046(mi)003:525: nags na ri dwags sogs tshigs bcad bcu bzhi /
NK046(mi)003:526: gnyis pa rnam rtog dor ba la'ang /
NK046(mi)003:530: 'jig rten 'di dang sogs tshigs bcad gcig /
NK046(mi)003:532: nang bud med kyi sred pa spangs pa /
NK046(mi)003:533: phyi rnyed sogs kyi sred pa spangs pa /
NK046(mi)003:534: dben pa'i yon tan dran pa dang gsum las /
NK046(mi)003:536: rgyu bsgrub dga' bar bsam pa /
NK046(mi)003:537: ngo bo mi gtsang ba yin pa /
NK046(mi)003:538: 'bras bu gnod pa mang bar bsam pa dang gsum las /
NK046(mi)003:540: pho nya pho nya sogs tshigs bcad gsum /
NK046(mi)003:542: gang zhig dang por sogs tshigs bcad nyer brgyad /
NK046(mi)003:544: de ltar mi gtsang sogs tshigs bcad brgyad /
NK046(mi)003:545: gnyis pa phyi rnyed sogs kyi sred pa spangs pa ni /
NK046(mi)003:546: bsags dang bsrung dang sogs tshigs bcad drug /
NK046(mi)003:547: gsum pa dben pa'i yon tan dran pa ni /
NK046(mi)003:548: de ltar 'dod la sogs tshigs bcad bzhi /
NK046(mi)003:549: gsum pa bsam gtan sgom pa dngos la /
NK046(mi)003:550: mtshams sbyar te mdor bstan pa /
NK046(mi)003:551: bsam gtan sgom tshul rgyas par bshad pa /
NK046(mi)003:552: ting nge 'dzin 'grub pa'i thabs la gdams pa dang gsum las /
NK046(mi)003:554: de la sogs pa'i sogs tshigs bcad gcig /
NK046(mi)003:556: bdag gzhan mnyam pa bsgom tshul dang /
NK046(mi)003:557: bdag gzhan barje ba bsgom tshul dang gnyis las /
NK046(mi)003:560: don bsdu ba dang gsum las /
NK046(mi)003:562: bdag dang gzhan du sogs tshigs bcad gcig /
NK046(mi)003:564: mnyam pa ji ltar bsgom tshul /
NK046(mi)003:565: de la rtsod pa spangs pa /
NK046(mi)003:566: de ltar goms pa'i phan yon dang gsum las /
NK046(mi)003:568: lag pa la sogs sogs tshigs bcad bcu gsum /
NK046(mi)003:570: snying rjes sdug bsngal sogs tshigs bcad gsum /
NK046(mi)003:572: de ltar rgyud ni sogs tshigs bcad gsum /
NK046(mi)003:573: gsum pa don bsdu ba ni /
NK046(mi)003:574: de bas ji ltar sogs tshigs bcad gcig /
NK046(mi)003:575: gnyis pa bdag gzhan barje ba la /
NK046(mi)003:576: rgyu mtshan brjod pas mdor bstan /
NK046(mi)003:577: de sgom tshul rgyas par bshad pa gnyis las /
NK046(mi)003:579: goms pa yis ni sogs tshigs bcad gsum /
NK046(mi)003:581: barje tshul spyir bstan pa dang /
NK046(mi)003:582: gnyen po'i khyad par bye brag tu bsgom pa /
NK046(mi)003:583: barjesa nas ji ltar bsgrub pa dang gsum las /
NK046(mi)003:587: bdag gzhan gtso bor byas pa'i skyon yon /
NK046(mi)003:588: des na nges par barje dgos par bstan pa dang bzhi las /
NK046(mi)003:590: ji ltar lag pa sogs tshigs bcad bdun /
NK046(mi)003:592: bdag lus gang la sogs tshigs bcad bzhi /
NK046(mi)003:594: gal te phyin na sogs tshigs bcad dgu /
NK046(mi)003:596: 'jig rten dag na sogs tshigs bcad drug /
NK046(mi)003:597: gnyis pa gnyen po'i khyad par bye brag tu sgom pa la'ang /
NK046(mi)003:599: rgyas par bshad pa gnyis las /
NK046(mi)003:601: dman sogs bdag tu sogs tshigs bcad gcig /
NK046(mi)003:603: dman pa dang barjesa nas phrag dog sgom pa dang /
NK046(mi)003:604: mnyam pa dang barjesa nas 'gran sems sgom pa dang /
NK046(mi)003:605: lhag pa dang barjesa nas nga rgyal sgom pa dang gsum las /
NK046(mi)003:607: 'di ni bkur byas sogs tshigs bcad drug /
NK046(mi)003:609: bdag dang mnyam la sogs tshigs bcad bzhi /
NK046(mi)003:611: nyon mongs 'di yang sogs tshigs bcad bzhi /
NK046(mi)003:612: gsum pa barjesa nas ji ltar sgrub pa la'ang /
NK046(mi)003:613: 'jam po'i sgo nas gdams pa dang /
NK046(mi)003:614: rtsub mo'i sgo nas tshar gcod pa gnyis las /
NK046(mi)003:616: yid khyod rang don sogs tshigs bcad bcu gsum /
NK046(mi)003:619: lus tshar bcad pa gnyis las /
NK046(mi)003:621: 'on te de ltar sogs tshigs bcad drug /
NK046(mi)003:623: ji lta ji ltar sogs tshigs bcad bcu gcig /
NK046(mi)003:624: gsum pa ting nge 'dzin 'grub pa'i thabs la gdams pa ni /
NK046(mi)003:625: de bas byis pa'i sogs tshigs bcad gsum /
NK046(mi)003:630: // gsum pa le'u dgu pa shes rab kyi le'u la /
NK046(mi)003:634: shes rab bskyed pa mdor bstan pa dang /
NK046(mi)003:635: de rgyas par bshad pa gnyis las /
NK046(mi)003:637: yan lag sogs tshigs bcad gcig /
NK046(mi)003:639: lta ba gtan la phab pa /
NK046(mi)003:640: sgom pas nyams su blangs pa /
NK046(mi)003:641: gtan tshigs kyis sgro 'dogs bcad pa /
NK046(mi)003:642: stong nyid rtogs pa'i byed las dang bzhi las /
NK046(mi)003:643: dang po la'ang bden gnyis kyi rnam pa bzhag pa /
NK046(mi)003:644: de la rtsod pa spangs pa /
NK046(mi)003:645: theg chen mchog tu sgrub pa dang gsum las /
NK046(mi)003:649: bden gnyis gtan la 'bebs pa'i gang zag dang gsum las /
NK046(mi)003:651: kun rdzob sogs tshigs rkang gnyis /
NK046(mi)003:653: don dam sogs rkang pa gnyis /
NK046(mi)003:655: de la sogs rkang pa drug /
NK046(mi)003:656: gnyis pa de la rtsod pa spangs pa la'ang gzhi bden gnyis la rtsod pa spangs pa /
NK046(mi)003:657: lam stong nyid la rtsod pa spangs pa /
NK046(mi)003:658: 'bras bu gzhan don la rtsod pa spangs pa dang gsum las /
NK046(mi)003:659: dang po la'ang 'jig rten phal pa'i rtsod spangs /
NK046(mi)003:660: nyan thos rnams kyi rtsod spangs /
NK046(mi)003:661: sems tsam rnams kyi rtsod pa spangs pa dang gsum las /
NK046(mi)003:663: gnyis ka yang ni sogs rkang pa drug /
NK046(mi)003:665: gzugs sogs mngon sum sogs tshigs bcad dgu dang rkang pa gnyis /
NK046(mi)003:667: gang tshe 'khrul pa'ang sogs tshigs bcad bcu bzhi dang rkang pa gnyis /
NK046(mi)003:668: gnyis pa lam stong nyid la rtsod pa spangs pa la'ang /
NK046(mi)003:672: sgyu ma lta bur sogs tshigs bcad gsum /
NK046(mi)003:674: gang tshe gang zhig sogs tshigs bcad gnyis /
NK046(mi)003:675: gsum pa 'bras bu gzhan don la rtsod pa spangs pa ni /
NK046(mi)003:676: yid bzhin nor bu sogs tshigs bcad lnga /
NK046(mi)003:677: gsum pa theg chen mchog tu sgrub pa la'ang /
NK046(mi)003:678: lung theg chen bkar sgrub pa dang /
NK046(mi)003:679: lam stong nyid gnyen por sgrub pa gnyis las /
NK046(mi)003:681: bden pa mthong bas sogs tshigs bcad bcu gnyis /
NK046(mi)003:683: rmongs bas sdug bsngal sogs tshigs bcad lnga /
NK046(mi)003:684: gnyis pa bsgom pas nyams su blangs pa la'ang /
NK046(mi)003:685: gang zag gi bdag med sgom tshul dang /
NK046(mi)003:686: chos kyi bdag med sgom tshul te gnyis las /
NK046(mi)003:688: lhan skyes kyi bdag stong par sgom tshul dang /
NK046(mi)003:689: kun brtag gi bdag stong par sgom tshul dang gnyis las /
NK046(mi)003:691: so dang skra sen sogs tshigs bcad gsum /
NK046(mi)003:693: bdag shes par 'dod pa dgag pa dang /
NK046(mi)003:694: bdag bem por 'dod pa dgag pa dang /
NK046(mi)003:695: bdag med pa'i don la rtsod pa spangs pa dang gsum las /
NK046(mi)003:697: gal te sgra yi sogs tshigs bcad brgyad /
NK046(mi)003:699: sems med pa yang sogs tshigs bcad gnyis /
NK046(mi)003:701: bdag med na las 'bras mi 'thad pa'i rtsod spangs /
NK046(mi)003:702: bdag med na snying rje mi 'thad pa'i rtsod spangs /
NK046(mi)003:703: btags pa'i bdag mi 'gog par bstan pa dang gsum las /
NK046(mi)003:705: gal te bdag ni sogs tshigs bcad lnga /
NK046(mi)003:707: gal te sems can sogs tshigs bcad gcig /
NK046(mi)003:709: sems can med 'bras sogs tshigs bcad gnyis /
NK046(mi)003:710: gnyis pa chos kyi bdag med sgom tshul la /
NK046(mi)003:711: lus dran pa nye bar bzhag pa dang /
NK046(mi)003:712: tshor ba dran pa nye bar bzhag pa dang /
NK046(mi)003:713: sems dran pa nye bar bzhag pa dang /
NK046(mi)003:714: chos dran pa nye bar bzhag pa sgom tshul dang bzhi las /
NK046(mi)003:717: yan lag bye brag tu brtags pa /
NK046(mi)003:718: des na lus la chags pa spangs dgos par bstan pa dang gsum las /
NK046(mi)003:720: lus ni rkang pa sogs tshigs bcad bdun dang rkang pa gcig /
NK046(mi)003:722: de bzhin sor mo'i sogs tshigs bcad gnyis /
NK046(mi)003:724: de ltar rmi lam sogs tshigs bcad gcig /
NK046(mi)003:726: tshong ba'i ngo bo la brtags pa /
NK046(mi)003:727: tshor ba'i rgyu la brtags pa /
NK046(mi)003:728: tshor ba'i 'bras bu la brtags pa /
NK046(mi)003:729: tshor ba po la brtags pa dang bzhi las /
NK046(mi)003:731: sdug bsngal de nyid sogs tshigs bcad lnga /
NK046(mi)003:733: gal te dbang don sogs tshigs bcad lnga /
NK046(mi)003:735: gang tshe tshor po sogs tshigs bcad gcig /
NK046(mi)003:737: mthong ba'am ni sogs tshigs bcad gsum /
NK046(mi)003:738: gsum pa sems dran pa nye bar bzhag pa la'ang /
NK046(mi)003:739: sems rang bzhin med par brtags pa dang /
NK046(mi)003:740: sems skye ba med par brtags pa gnyis las /
NK046(mi)003:742: yid ni dbang rnams sogs tshigs bcad gnyis /
NK046(mi)003:744: shes bya las sngar sogs tshigs rkang pa drug /
NK046(mi)003:746: chos dran pa nyer bzhag dngos bshad pa dang /
NK046(mi)003:747: de la rtsod pa spangs pa dang gnyis las /
NK046(mi)003:749: de ltar chos rnams sogs rkang pa gnyis /
NK046(mi)003:751: bden gnyis mi 'thad pa'i rtsod spangs /
NK046(mi)003:752: gtan tshigs med pa'i rtsod spangs /
NK046(mi)003:753: rnam dpyod thug med du 'gyur ba'i rtsod spangs dang gsum las /
NK046(mi)003:755: gal te de ltar sogs tshigs bcad gnyis /
NK046(mi)003:757: rtog dang brtags par sogs tshigs bcad gcig /
NK046(mi)003:759: gang tshe rnam par sogs tshigs bcad gnyis /
NK046(mi)003:760: gsum pa gtan tshigs kyis sgro 'dogs gcod pa la /
NK046(mi)003:761: dngos por smra ba'i sgrub byed dgag pa dang /
NK046(mi)003:762: stong par smra ba'i sgrub byed bkod pa dang gnyis las /
NK046(mi)003:764: gang gi ltar na sogs tshigs bcad lnga /
NK046(mi)003:766: rgyu la dpyod pa rdo rje'i gzeg ma /
NK046(mi)003:767: ngo bo la dpyod pa rten 'brel chen mo /
NK046(mi)003:768: 'bras bu la dpyod pa yod med skye 'gog dang gsum las /
NK046(mi)003:770: rgyu med las skye bar 'dod pa dgag pa dang /
NK046(mi)003:771: gzhan las skye bar 'dod ba dgag pa dang /
NK046(mi)003:772: bdag las skye bar 'dod pa dgag pa dang /
NK046(mi)003:773: don bsdu ba dang bzhi las /
NK046(mi)003:775: re zhig 'jig rten sogs tshigs bcad gnyis /
NK046(mi)003:777: gzhan mi rtag pa las skye ba dang /
NK046(mi)003:778: rtag pa las skye bar 'dod pa gnyis las /
NK046(mi)003:779: snga ma bshad zin na sa /
NK046(mi)003:781: dbang phyug 'gro sogs tshigs bcad brgyad dang rkang pa gnyis /
NK046(mi)003:784: bdag skye dngos dgag pa dang gnyis las /
NK046(mi)003:786: gtso bo rtag pa sogs tshigs bcad brgyad /
NK046(mi)003:788: gal te med pa sogs tshigs bcad drug dang rkang ba gnyis /
NK046(mi)003:789: bzhi pa don bsdu ba ni /
NK046(mi)003:790: de bas sogs rkang pa drug /
NK046(mi)003:791: gnyis pa rten 'brel chen mo'i gtan tshigs ni /
NK046(mi)003:792: rmongs pas sogs rkang pa bcu /
NK046(mi)003:793: gsum pa 'bras bu la dpyod pa yod med skye 'gog ni /
NK046(mi)003:794: dngos po sogs tshigs bcad drug /
NK046(mi)003:795: bzhi pa stong nyid rtogs pa'i byed las la /
NK046(mi)003:796: rang don du chos brgyad mgo snyoms pa dang /
NK046(mi)003:797: gzhan don du brtse ba'i snying rje rtsol med du 'byung ba gnyis las /
NK046(mi)003:799: de ltar sogs tshigs bcad gsum dang rkang ba gnyis /
NK046(mi)003:801: bdag nyid sogs tshigs bcad bcu gsum dang rkang pa gnyis /
NK046(mi)003:806: // bzhi pa de ltar spel ba'i 'bras bu gzhan don du bsngo ba'i le'u la /
NK046(mi)003:807: bsngo ba mdor bsdus te bstan pa dang /
NK046(mi)003:808: de rgyas par bshad pa gnyis las /
NK046(mi)003:810: bdag gis byang chub sogs tshigs bcad gcig /
NK046(mi)003:812: gzhan don phan dang bde ba'i rgyur bsngo ba dang /
NK046(mi)003:813: rang don byang chub spyod pa'i rgyur bsngo ba dang /
NK046(mi)003:814: gnyis don bstan pa dar rgyas su bsngo ba dang gsum las /
NK046(mi)003:816: dman pa dang bral bar bsngo ba dang /
NK046(mi)003:817: mchog gi dgongs pa rdzogs par bsngo ba dang gnyis las /
NK046(mi)003:819: khams gsum sems can spyi la khyab pa'i sdug bsngal dang bral bar bsngo ba dang /
NK046(mi)003:820: ngan song gsum sogs 'gro ba so so'i sdug bsngal
NK046(mi)003:821: bye brag dang bral bar bsngo ba dang gnyis las
NK046(mi)003:823: phyogs rnams sogs tshigs bcad gnyis /
NK046(mi)003:825: 'jig rten khams na sogs tshigs bcad bzhi bcu zhe bzhis bstan /
NK046(mi)003:826: gnyis pa mchog gi dgongs pa rdzogs par bsngo ba ni /
NK046(mi)003:827: sems can sogs tshigs bcad gnyis dang rkang pa gnyis /
NK046(mi)003:828: gnyis pa rang don byang chub spyod pa'i rgyur bsngo ba ni /
NK046(mi)003:829: bdag kyang sogs tshigs bcad drug /
NK046(mi)003:830: gsum pa gnyis don bstan pa dar rgyas su bsngo ba ni /
NK046(mi)003:831: 'gro ba'i sdug bsngal sogs tshigs bcad gcig gis bstan /
NK046(mi)003:832: gsum pa brtsams pa mthar phyin pa /
NK046(mi)003:833: mjug yongs rdzogs pa'i don ston pa la /
NK046(mi)003:834: bka' drin dran pa'i phyag bya ba dang /
NK046(mi)003:836: gang gis brtsams pa'i mdzad byang /
NK046(mi)003:837: mjug lo ts+aa ba'i 'gyur byang bshad pa dang bzhi las /
NK046(mi)003:839: gang gi drin gyis sogs tshigs bcad gcig /
NK046(mi)003:845: byang chub sems dpa'i sogs nas slob dpon shan+ta de was mdzad pa rdzogs so //
NK046(mi)003:847: rgya gar gyi mkhan po sogs kyis bstan to //
NK046(mi)003:849: // sangs rgyas dang byang chub sems dpa' thams cad la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK046(mi)003:850: zab dang rgya che theg pa mchog gzhung las //
NK046(mi)003:851: zab mo lta ba'i don mchog ston pa'i bka' //
NK046(mi)003:852: shes rab phar phyin rdo rje gcod pa dang //
NK046(mi)003:853: rgya chen spyod pa'i gnad kun yongs bsdus pa //
NK046(mi)003:854: sems dpa'i bstan bcos spyod gzhung sa bcad bcas //
NK046(mi)003:855: bka' bstan kun gyi gtsor gyur rnam gnyis kyi //
NK046(mi)003:856: dpe brgya'i phyi mor gyur pa'i par 'di dag /
NK046(mi)003:857: dam pa mchog gyur pradz+ny+aa'i mtshan can gyis //
NK046(mi)003:858: thugs bskyed rnam dag mkha' ltar dwangs bas bsgrubs //
NK046(mi)003:859: dge des rgyal bstan dar zhing rgyas pa dang //
NK046(mi)003:860: khyad par yun ring drin gyis legs skyong ba'i //
NK046(mi)003:861: pha ma dud 'gro'i skye gnas las thar te //
NK046(mi)003:862: lha mi'i rten las rnam grol mchog thob shog /
NK046(mi)003:863: sa bcad spar byang dang bcas pa dpal sprul rin po ches mdzad pa dge'o //
